          "text": "In the general discussion channel, several community members introduced themselves and shared their work. An AI Engineer and Security Researcher named Marsel posted a detailed introduction highlighting expertise in agentic workflows, Web3 security, custom plugin development for elizaOS projects, and automation using Python and FastAPI. He expressed interest in developer tasks, plugin building, and security audits for agentic workflows. Separately, a representative from Intuition Box, a developer ecosystem, reached out to the community about two upcoming bounties and expressed interest in collaborating with the elizaOS developer community, asking for the appropriate contact or permission to share the bounties publicly. Odilitime also shared a link to an upcoming Twitter Space event.",
